	(text "Gate drive network for STP20NM60FP:\n- Vdrive = 15 V (from IR2136)\n- Series gate resistor Rg = 15-22 Ω\n- Internal MOSFET gate resistance Rint ≈ 1.6 Ω\n- Total gate charge Qg ≈ 40-50 nC\n- Target switching ~100 ns → Ig ≈ 0.5-0.7 A\n- Diode for asymmetrical turn-on/off\n- Purpose: Limit di/dt, reduce ringing/EMI\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 275.844 111.506 0)
		(effects
