	)
	(text "470pF + 1kΩ ITRIP Filte\nτ = RC = 1kΩ × 470pF = 470ns\nt_rise (10-90%) ≈ 1.0μs\nt_90 (settling) ≈ 1.1μs\nf_cutoff = 1/(2πRC) = 339kHz"
